braindump lets the user enter items that need to get done in a freeformish way and then processes them into actions/projects.


Let the user type in something like the following.  try to divine what's a task.
for extra prettieness use xmlhttprequest to show the user what we're doing as they type.






    pick up laundry on tuesday

    write proposal for jesse@fsck.com

    build gtd system

